utton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527152\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527152\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 20, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104eig1665702618823.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eig1665702618823.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eig1665702618823.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"eig1665702618823\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      U-Bar\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The U-Bar is a multi-functional control that identifies the current object, and is used to locate and open or select development objects. U-Bars are found in the IDE header and in the Resource Browser.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eig1665702618823__p_d5030e1_d5031e1_d5032e1\">The U-Bar has a defined syntax for specifying objects. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">cpt:MY_COMPONENT/ent:AN_ENTITY.MODEL/fld:FLD1</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eig1665702618823__p_d5033e1_d5034e1_d5035e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"blx1694688356882.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/blx1694688356882.html\" title=\"The U-Bar supports a defined syntax for navigating to specific objects, and locations within objects.\">U-Bar Syntax</a>.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eig1665702618823__section_c3g_gpl_lcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d615448e67\">Main U-Bar </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eig1665702618823__p_d5039e1_d5040e1_d5041e1\">The Main U-Bar, located in the IDE header, is used to:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"eig1665702618823__ul_lrx_hpl_lcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"eig1665702618823__li_d2036e1_d2037e1_d2038e1\">Open development objects for editing. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"eig1665702618823__li_d2039e1_d2040e1_d2041e1\">Navigate to a subobject or property, editor worksheet,\n          or window. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"eig1665702618823__li_d2042e1_d2043e1_d2044e1\">Display the URL of the current main development object.\n        </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eig1665702618823__p_d5042e1_d5043e1_d5044e1\">To open an object for editing, click\n          <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Browse</span>, then select the object type and enter an object name. As\n        you type, suggested objects are listed in a drop-down box.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eig1665702618823__p_d5045e1_d5046e1_d5047e1\">To navigate to a specific property, code position,\n        worksheet, and window, you can enter a URL that specifies the object and where it should be\n        opened. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"eig1665702618823__pre_nrx_hpl_lcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">cpt:ORDERFRM/ent:ORDERS.SALES/fld:BTN_ADD_LINE/prop:USCRIPT/pos:3,4 worksheet=script window=2</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eig1665702618823__section_hrl_mpl_lcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d615448e101\">Resource Browser U-Bar </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eig1665702618823__p_d5054e1_d5055e1_d5056e1\">The U-Bar in the Resource Browser is used to filter the\n        objects shown in the current tab so that you can select and add them to the current object.\n        In the Component Editor, you can use the U-Bar in the Model tab to search for modeled\n        entities and browse the fields or sub-entities of a specific modeled entity.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eig1665702618823__p_d5057e1_d5058e1_d5059e1\">For more\n        information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yed1704964703330.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yed1704964703330.html\" title=\"The number of objects available for selection in the Resource Browser may be very large, so you can filter the content in a variety of ways, depending on context.\">Filter and Search for Objects in Resource Browser</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uoo1665702618603.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uoo1665702618603.html\" title=\"Smart suggestions are a Uniface feature that enable search and filtering functionality on the basis of object name and description. This makes it easier and faster to find an object that you want to open, edit, or use in a given context.\">Smart Suggestions and Filtering</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eig1665702618823__section_qjz_jq1_4cc\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"eig1665702618823__table_evy_ypg_q3c\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Related learning videos</span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"eig1665702618823__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__1\">Title</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"eig1665702618823__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__2\">link</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"eig1665702618823__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__1\">Using U-Bar</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"eig1665702618823__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://vimeo.com/showcase/10552636/video/870268109\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"Click to watch or listen U-Bar video\" class=\"image\" id=\"eig1665702618823__image_pff_pqw_q3c\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/My_Video_Button.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/></a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527152\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527152\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "U-Bar Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 20, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 U-Bar The U-Bar is a multi-functional control that identifies the current object, and is used to locate and open or select development objects. U-Bars are found in the IDE header and in the Resource Browser. The U-Bar has a defined syntax for specifying objects. For example: cpt:MY_COMPONENT/ent:AN_ENTITY.MODEL/fld:FLD1 Copy For more information, see U-Bar Syntax . Main U-Bar The Main U-Bar, located in the IDE header, is used to: Open development objects for editing. Navigate to a subobject or property, editor worksheet, or window. Display the URL of the current main development object. To open an object for editing, click Browse , then select the object type and enter an object name. As you type, suggested objects are listed in a drop-down box. To navigate to a specific property, code position, worksheet, and window, you can enter a URL that specifies the object and where it should be opened. For example: cpt:ORDERFRM/ent:ORDERS.SALES/fld:BTN_ADD_LINE/prop:USCRIPT/pos:3,4 worksheet=script window=2 Copy Resource Browser U-Bar The U-Bar in the Resource Browser is used to filter the objects shown in the current tab so that you can select and add them to the current object. In the Component Editor, you can use the U-Bar in the Model tab to search for modeled entities and browse the fields or sub-entities of a specific modeled entity. For more information, see Filter and Search for Objects in Resource Browser and Smart Suggestions and Filtering . Table 1. Related learning videos Title link Using U-Bar Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}